Detailed Description

Configuration parameters for CSC.

struct Vps_CscConfig

Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_CscConfig::bypass

Flag to indicate whether CSC to be bypassed or not.

Vps_CscCoeff* Vps_CscConfig::coeff

Set of user provided coefficients. Null if pre-calculated coefficients is to be used.

UInt32 Vps_CscConfig::mode

Used to select one of pre-calculated coefficient sets. Used only if coeff is null. For valid values see Vps_CscMode.
